Program: Crossing Continents
Title: India's Whistleblowers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b017528n
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 21 Nov 2011
Rupa Jha investigates how local-level campaigners against corruption in India face threats and violence - despite promises that the government will stamp out graft. She tells the stories of two whistleblowers in two different states who faced ferocious intimidation after they tried to challenge powerful individuals on the take. Producer: Ed Butler. Show less